    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in a state of absolute preservation, reflecting a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin appointments, adheres to the highest benchmarks of excellence. We invite the most discerning buyers to inspect this masterwork of engineering and aesthetic integrity. Experience a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market.",
