    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been pampered its whole life and is in truly spectacular shape\u2014spotless inside and out! It drives like an absolute dream, honestly just like it did the day it was bought. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much. It's a total gem, so come grab it before it's gone!",
