    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather is supple with zero bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several trim pieces. Mechanically, it is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive service history from the authorized dealership. With ultra-low mileage and a non-smoker, pet-free history, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in its purest form.",
      "price": 46500.0,
