    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely flawless condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s incredibly clean inside and out\u2014seriously, it's pristine. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look and fall in love!",
