    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a documented VANOS system overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement to ensure peak torsional rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement, feeding power through a refreshed limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its razor-sharp handling characteristics via original-spec dampers and bushings, preserving the iconic 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in Carbon Black, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no signs of environmental degradation. This is an investment-grade example for the mechanical purist.",
